We enhance human potential through robotics

18.description:
At Koteos Robotics, we are committed to leading innovation in the field of robotics, driving human potential to new heights. Since our founding in 2014, we have been dedicated to developing advanced solutions that integrate robotic technology to enhance people's lives and work.

Our focus lies in three main areas of cutting-edge robotics:

Wearable Robotics (Exoskeletons): We design and manufacture state-of-the-art exoskeletons that enhance users' mobility and strength, providing innovative solutions for industrial  environments.

Collaborative Robotics (Human-Operated Load Arms): Our collaborative robotic arms are designed to work closely with human operators, increasing efficiency and safety in manufacturing and logistics environments.

Telerobotics: With our advanced telerobotics technology, we enable operators to remotely control robots to perform precise tasks in hazardous or hard-to-reach environments, enhancing productivity and reducing human risk.

At Koteos Robotics, we believe in the power of robotic technology to improve people's lives and transform the way we work. Our team consists of passionate experts who strive to deliver innovative, high-quality solutions in every project.

Join us on our journey to drive the future of robotics and discover new ways to empower human potential!

12.short_description: Gitcolony simplifies software creation by streamlining the code review and QA processes.

18.description:
Gitcolony allows teams to build bulletproof software faster. By streamlining the code review process, automating QA, adding a layer of business rules to code management and incorporating gamification, Gitcolony allows teams to build better software in an efficient and amusing way.

Gitcolony encourages developers to share early feedback, do partial reviews, reduce rework and leverage the knowledge of the whole group. Teams become more efficient by adding visibility to the process.

With Gitcolony, teams are able to:

* set up and enforce your own custom rules to keep your code quality under control. Gitcolony helps you reinforce your code review policies and best practices your team follows informally.
* collaborate with your team in real time, performing progressive checks to avoid titanic reviews
* encourage software developers with performance rankings and gamification techniques
* integrate QA and development processes to minimize coordination friction between both teams
